  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eNestled in the scenic surroundings of Pilar, Argentina, \u003ca href=\"https://atelierm.ar/en/projects/nirvana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNirvana House\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e by \u003ca href=\"https://atelierm.ar/es\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAtelierM\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e reimagines the boundaries of residential architecture. Overlooking a polo field, this 3,767-square-foot home combines innovation, sustainability, and a commitment to blending with its environment. The result is a home that transcends mere functionality, offering its inhabitants a seamless connection with the natural world.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566723\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566723\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-810x810.jpg\" alt=\"Modern house with green roofs and a pool, surrounded by grass and trees, next to a large open field.\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-810x810.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-800x800.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-100x100.jpg 100w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt the heart of Nirvana House lies an unconventional concept – a three-level garden that appears to rise organically from the earth, topped off with a lush green roof. This detail ensures the home integrates effortlessly into the surrounding terrain, creating a dialogue between structure and environment. The design’s flowing lines and organic contours mirror the undulating topography, forming a residence that feels as though it has grown from the ground itself.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566724\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566724\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3-810x455.jpg\" alt=\"Aerial view of a modern, eco-friendly house with a green roof, a garden, and a rectangular swimming pool, situated near a paved road with parked cars and surrounded by grassy areas.\" width=\"810\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3-810x455.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3-800x449.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3-768x431.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566725\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566725\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern concrete house with large windows and a green roof, surrounded by grass and trees, under a blue sky with scattered clouds.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConcrete and wood were deliberately selected as primary materials, chosen for their durability, low maintenance, and capacity to develop a natural patina over time. These materials not only enhance the structure’s longevity but also deepen its visual and textural connection to the landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566726\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566726\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern house with a green roof and wooden exterior, surrounded by grass and trees under a cloudy sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566727\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566727\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-6-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern building with a green roof and large window is surrounded by trees and grass. Steps lead up to the entrance.\" width=\"810\" heig