 home with its verdant surroundings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566736\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566736\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-15-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern building interior with a staircase leading down, featuring concrete and wooden walls, large glass windows, and a view of outdoor greenery and distant structures.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-15-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566737\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566737\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-16-810x692.jpg\" alt=\"Curved concrete hallway with a metal railing and wooden wall, leading to a staircase. Large window offers a view of greenery and trees outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"692\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-16-810x692.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-16-800x683.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-16-768x656.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Nirvana-House-Argentina-AtelierM-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566738\" r